        <zone forceUpdate='true' h='14650' id='42' type-v2='text' w='17730' x='82086' y='12950'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='10'>Key Insights</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Bold'>1. August records peak admissions (4,211 patients) while February sees the lowest (3,716), indicating seasonal health patterns</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Bold'>2. Johnson PLC leads hospital revenue at $1.08M, with top 10 hospitals showing competitive performance within a $0.26M range</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Bold'>3. Cigna is the top insurance provider at $287.1M - revenue evenly split across all 5 providers indicating strong multi-insurer coverage</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Bold'>4. All 6 medical conditions show uniform patient distribution (9,185–9,308) with Diabetes generating highest revenue at $238.54M</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Bold'>5. Emergency admissions average longest stay at 15.6 days while Elective billing is highest at $25.60K</run>
          </formatted-text>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='solid' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='1' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
